{"tid":2169244,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[NBA] 字句中反過來歧視白人？Harrell在Doncic面前得分後噴\"Bxxxx Axx White Boy\"","createTime":"2020-08-22T10:34:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T11:23:09.000Z","uid":201494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e1394b61872d0edc5c03d41ecde0faf36f1ac4c7","tid":2169244,"uid":201494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T10:34:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://basketball.fanpiece.com/m/victorli/c1383220.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbasketball.fanpiece.com%2Fm%2Fvictorli%2Fc1383220.html&d=aFiO92UEzPWfS5u3FViI6S9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=302f7f1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://basketball.fanpiece.com/m/victorli/c1383220.html</a><br />\n<br />\n在洛杉磯快艇對陣達拉斯獨行俠的三場系列賽事中，雙方各不相讓多番發生爭執。今天快艇Montrezl Harrell和達拉斯獨行俠Luka Doncic又再有口角。<br />\n<br />\n在第一節5:23 Montrezl Harrell在籃下接到Paul George的傳球後被Luka Doncic和Tim Hardaway Jr.包夾。雖然二人合力，但是力量和高度都不及Montrezl Harrell。Harrell撞開Doncic製造空間上籃成功，在回防期間噴垃圾話說：「Bxxxx Axx White Boy！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pJ_hrHmgTAM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpJ_hrHmgTAM&d=aFiO92UEzPWfS5u3FViI6S9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=1048b794\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pJ_hrHmgTAM</a>"},{"pid":"d43329e7d4c26eb644cc6aeaecca24ebf8da11d2","tid":2169244,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T10:35:11.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"5614dbb1f786b5875bf327e0e956c8033a779101","tid":2169244,"uid":79117,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T10:35:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f89824a43e21bf5ff11f9ad825037d14ee157f8","tid":2169244,"uid":201494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5614dbb1f786b5875bf327e0e956c8033a779101","tid":2169244,"uid":79117,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T10:35:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T10:39:12.000Z","msg":"無錯"},{"pid":"dc50661dd042c1dc46048cd23f19498e9ff15e3b","tid":2169244,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T10:41:54.000Z","msg":"Black Ate White Boy<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b20aa2f12358bba2ac7f7c915961af2297a11b46","tid":2169244,"uid":186174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T10:53:18.000Z","msg":"好似話會停賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6178b477ff11baaa5ed238a8596260f3efb0dca6","tid":2169244,"uid":201494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T11:17:57.000Z","msg":"據悉，在得知Harrell的所作所為之後，獨行俠當場就向當值裁判進行了抗議，但是裁判並沒有給予任何回應，據報導，獨行俠已經準備好材料，進行上訴，而目的只有一個，就是嚴懲Harrell。<br />\n<br />\n隨後，NBA聯盟抵抗族歧視委員會也在賽后發布了聲明，會對此事進行認真調查，如果情況屬實，那麼Harrell將會面臨包括罰款、停賽等多項處罰。"},{"pid":"c4516096481df62a794418b249d2a9d6686d7c5f","tid":2169244,"uid":54959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T11:21:15.000Z","msg":"黑人大晒，當trash talk 就無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a05eb4894fb4c3b86d3135f60e02c314e01dd5a2","tid":2169244,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T11:23:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}